<div class="govuk-panel govuk-panel--confirmation">
  <h1 class="govuk-panel__title">
    Walkthrough complete
  </h1>
  <div class="govuk-panel__body">
    You've explored the Back Office Planning System used by UK councils
  </div>
</div>

<p class="govuk-body-l govuk-!-margin-top-6">
  You've just experienced the <a href="https://opendigitalplanning.org/back-office-planning-system-bops" class="govuk-link">Back Office Planning System (BOPS)</a> — the same system used by councils like Lambeth, Southwark, and Buckinghamshire to process real planning applications. In 15 minutes, you've seen what would take weeks of procurement and vendor demos.
</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">What you've learned</h2>

<div class="ndx-takeaway-grid">
  <div class="ndx-takeaway-card">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
      <span class="ndx-takeaway-card__icon">&#x1f3d7;</span>
      Structured workflow
    </h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      BOPS enforces a consistent validation, consultation, assessment, and determination workflow. Every application follows the same process, reducing errors and ensuring nothing is missed.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s" style="color: #505a5f; font-weight: 700;">
      Value: Consistent quality across thousands of applications per year
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ndx-takeaway-card">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
      <span class="ndx-takeaway-card__icon">&#x1f4ca;</span>
      Dashboard-driven management
    </h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Case officers see their assigned workload with days-to-determination deadlines. Team leaders can monitor all cases and identify bottlenecks before statutory deadlines are missed.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s" style="color: #505a5f; font-weight: 700;">
      Value: Real-time visibility into team workload and statutory compliance
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ndx-takeaway-card">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
      <span class="ndx-takeaway-card__icon">&#x1f310;</span>
      Public transparency
    </h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      The applicants portal gives residents real-time visibility into planning applications affecting their area. Map views, consultation dates, and application tracking reduce phone calls and FOI requests.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s" style="color: #505a5f; font-weight: 700;">
      Value: Fewer enquiries, better public engagement, statutory consultation compliance
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ndx-takeaway-card">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
      <span class="ndx-takeaway-card__icon">&#x1f527;</span>
      Open source platform
    </h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      BOPS is developed by the <a href="https://opendigitalplanning.org/back-office-planning-system-bops" class="govuk-link">Open Digital Planning programme</a> and freely available. No licence fees, no vendor lock-in. Multiple councils contribute to and benefit from shared development.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s" style="color: #505a5f; font-weight: 700;">
      Value: Zero licence costs, community-driven development, shared innovation
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">Production readiness</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">
  This demo runs the same codebase used in production by multiple UK councils. For a full deployment, you'd additionally want:
</p>

<table class="govuk-table">
  <thead class="govuk-table__head">
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Feature</th>
      <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Demo status</th>
      <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Production requirement</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody class="govuk-table__body">
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header">Custom domain</th>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">CloudFront URL</td>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">planning.yourcouncil.gov.uk</td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header">GOV.UK Notify</th>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Disabled (demo)</td>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Email notifications, 2FA codes</td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header">OS Maps</th>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Optional API key</td>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Full OS Vector Tiles integration</td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header">Data migration</th>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">35 sample applications</td>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Import from existing planning system</td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header">Backup</th>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Aurora automated (24hr sandbox)</td>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Point-in-time recovery, cross-region</td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header">Integrations</th>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Standalone</td>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">PlanX submission, GIS, document management</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<div class="govuk-inset-text govuk-!-margin-top-4">
